    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it an excellent choice for a reliable and comfortable daily driver. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly, reflecting its solid mechanical health. While the interior is clean and the exterior paint retains a nice shine, there are a few minor cosmetic blemishes and light wear consistent with careful use. Overall, it is a dependable car that offers great performance and is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
