    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition and presents exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no scratches, dents, or chips. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the leather upholstery is supple and free of wear, and all electronic features and climate controls function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in peak condition with a full service history, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience that feels brand new. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously maintained vehicle that requires nothing but a new owner.",
      "price": 49500.0,
